### Comparison to Alternatives

| Tool | Approach |
|---|---|
| Arthur Shield | Proxy-based, enterprise focus, bidirectional |
| Guardrails AI | Python library, in-process |
| LlamaGuard (Meta) | Open-source model-based classifier |
| Nemo Guardrails (NVIDIA) | Dialogue flow control |
| Lakera Guard | API-based, prompt injection focus |

Arthur Shield's differentiation is its **enterprise-grade proxy architecture**, **deep observability**, and **self-hosted deployment option** — making it appealing where data residency and audit trails matter.

